#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.parallel"
msgstr "# triton.language.parallel"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:2
msgid "## 1. 函数概述"
msgstr "## 1. Function Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:4
msgid "`parallel` 是一个专门用于多核心并行执行的迭代器，继承自 `range` 类，提供显式的多核心并行语义。"
msgstr "`parallel` is an iterator specifically designed for multi-core parallel execution, inheriting from the `range` class and providing explicit multi-core parallel semantics."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.parallel(arg1, arg2=None, step=None, num_stages=None,\n"
"                         loop_unroll_factor=None, bind_sub_block: bool = False,\n"
"                         _semantic=None)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:8
msgid "## 2. 规格"
msgstr "## 2. Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数 | 类型 | 默认值 | 含义说明 |\n"
"|------|------|--------|----------|\n"
"| `arg1` | `int` /`constexpr`| 必需 | 起始值（单参数时作为结束值，从0开始） |\n"
"| `arg2` | `int`/`constexpr` | - | 结束值（不包含在范围内） |\n"
"| `step` | `int` /`constexpr`| `1` | 每次迭代的步长增量 |\n"
"| `num_stages` | `int` | - | 流水线阶段数（同时执行的迭代数量） |\n"
"| `loop_unroll_factor` | `int` | - | 循环展开因子（<2表示不展开） |\n"
"| `bind_sub_block` | `bool` | `False` | **关键参数**：绑定到子块，启用多核心并行执行 |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Default | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|---------|-------------|\n"
"| `arg1` | `int` / `constexpr` | Required | Start value (when single parameter, used as end value, starting from 0) |\n"
"| `arg2` | `int` / `constexpr` | - | End value (not included in the range) |\n"
"| `step` | `int` / `constexpr` | `1` | Step increment per iteration |\n"
"| `num_stages` | `int` | - | Number of pipeline stages (number of iterations executed simultaneously) |\n"
"| `loop_unroll_factor` | `int` | - | Loop unroll factor (<2 means no unrolling) |\n"
"| `bind_sub_block` | `bool` | `False` | **Key parameter**: bind to sub-block, enable multi-core parallel execution |\n"
"| `_semantic` | - | - | Reserved parameter, external calls not supported for now |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/parallel.md:14
msgid ""
"> **注意**：`parallel` 相比于 `range` 移除了以下参数：\n"
">\n"
"> - `disallow_acc_multi_buffer`\n"
"> - `flatten`\n"
"> - `warp_specialize`\n"
"> - `disable_licm`\n"
msgstr ""
"> **Note**: `parallel` removes the following parameters compared to `range`:\n"
">\n"
"> - `disallow_acc_multi_buffer`\n"
"> - `flatten`\n"
"> - `warp_specialize`\n"
"> - `disable_licm`\n"

